				<article id="post-91552" class="post-91552 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-fellows-friday category-health tag-aunt-bertha tag-crisis tag-erine-gray tag-non-profits tag-social-services tag-ted-fellows tag-united-states clearfix has-thumbnail not-featured even top i-0" role="article">

					<header class="article-header">
	<a href="http://blog.ted.com/category/fellows-friday/" class="category-title">Fellows Friday</a> <a href="http://blog.ted.com/initiatives/ted-fellows/" class="tag-initiative">TED Fellows</a>	<h1 class="single-title" itemprop="headline">Need help? Aunt Bertha helps people in need find social services in their&nbsp;area</h1>

	<div class="meta clearfix">
		<div class="author-pic"><img src="http://images.ted.com/images/ted/182709_165x165.jpg" id="author-image" width="37" height="37"></div>
		<div class="author-desc">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.ted.com/author/mmechinita/">Karen Eng</a> <br><time datetime="2014-08-29">August 29, 2014 at 2:20 pm EDT</time>
		</div>
		<div class="share">
			<div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"><div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-icon sd-sharing"><div class="sd-content"><ul><li class="share-twitter"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-twitter sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/08/29/need-help-ask-aunt-bertha-erine-gray-helps-people-in-need-find-social-services-in-their-area/?share=twitter" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Twitter" id="sharing-twitter-91552"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-facebook"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-facebook sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/08/29/need-help-ask-aunt-bertha-erine-gray-helps-people-in-need-find-social-services-in-their-area/?share=facebook" target="_blank" title="Share on Facebook" id="sharing-facebook-91552"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-linkedin"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-linkedin sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/08/29/need-help-ask-aunt-bertha-erine-gray-helps-people-in-need-find-social-services-in-their-area/?share=linkedin" target="_blank" title="Click to share on LinkedIn" id="sharing-linkedin-91552"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-reddit"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-reddit sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/08/29/need-help-ask-aunt-bertha-erine-gray-helps-people-in-need-find-social-services-in-their-area/?share=reddit" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Reddit"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-email"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-email sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/08/29/need-help-ask-aunt-bertha-erine-gray-helps-people-in-need-find-social-services-in-their-area/?share=email" target="_blank" title="Click to email this to a friend"><span></span></a></li><li><a href="#" class="sharing-anchor sd-button share-more"><span>More</span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul><div class="sharing-hidden"><div class="inner" style="display: none;"><ul><li class="share