<article id="post-90783" class="post-90783 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-in-brief tag-jr tag-steve-case tag-ted-news tag-ted-news-in-brief has-thumbnail not-featured odd i-15 clearfix" role="article">

			<a href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/06/27/steve-case-takes-a-road-and-other-ted-community-news/" data-slug="steve-case-takes-a-road-and-other-ted-community-news" class="post-thumbnail">
			<img src='http://i0.wp.com/tedconfblog.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/jr-pantheon.jpg?resize=283%2C212' width='283' height='212' alt='Steve Case takes a road trip, JR turns the Panthéon Inside Out, plus insights into what’s killing&nbsp;bees' />		</a>
		
			<h4>
			<a class="category" href="http://blog.ted.com/category/in-brief/" data-slug="in-brief" >
				In Brief			</a>
		</h4>
	
	<h2 class="post-title">
		<a href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/06/27/steve-case-takes-a-road-and-other-ted-community-news/" data-slug="steve-case-takes-a-road-and-other-ted-community-news">
			Steve Case takes a road trip, JR turns the Panthéon Inside Out, plus insights into what’s killing&nbsp;bees		</a>
	</h2>

	<div class="meta">
		<div class="meta__author">
			<span>By</span>
			<a href="http://blog.ted.com/author/kateted/">
				Kate Torgovnick May			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="meta__date">
			<span>on</span>
			<time datetime="2014-06-27" pubdate >
				Jun 27, 2014			</time>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="excerpt">
		<p>Below, just a few members of the TED community who made headlines this week. Longtime TEDster Steve Case is hitting the road this summer to find and invest in start-ups that may otherwise be overlooked. His &#8220;Rise of the Rest Road Trip&#8221; kicked off in Detroit this week and will continue on to Pittsburg, Cincinnati <a class="read-more" title="Read more" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/06/27/steve-case-takes-a-road-and-other-ted-community-news/">[<span>&hellip;</span>]</a></p>
	</div>

</article>
			
				
<article id="post-87529" class="post-87529 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-live-from-ted2014 tag-alexander-mclean tag-aziz-abu-sarah tag-aziza-chaouni tag-bora-yoon tag-dan-visconti tag-erine-gray tag-janet-iwasa tag-jorge-manes-rubio tag-lars-jan tag-robert-simpson tag-sergei-lupashin tag-shohini-ghose tag-shubhendu-sharma tag-ted2014-fellows-talks-session-1-recap tag-usman-riaz tag-ziyah-gafic has-thumbnail not-featured even i-16 clearfix" role="article">

			<a href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/03/17/from-3d-animated-molecules-to-tethered-kite-copters-a-recap-of-the-ted2014-fellows-talks-session-1/" data-slug="from-3d-animated-molecules-to-tethered-kite-copters-a-recap-of-the-ted2014-fellows-talks-session-1" class="post-thumbnail">
			<img src='http://i2.wp.com/tedconfblog.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/ted2014_rl_rl5d1340.jpg?resize=283%2C212' width='283' height='212' alt='From 3D animated molecules to tethered kite-copters: A recap of the TED2014 Fellows Talks, Session&nbsp;1' />		</a>
		
			<h4>
			<a class="category" href="http://blog.ted.com/category/live-from-ted2014/" data-slug="live-from-ted2014" >
				Live from TED2014			</a>
		</h4>
	
	<h2 class="post-title">
		<a href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/03/17/from-3d-animated-molecules-to-tethered-kite-copters-a-recap-of-the-ted2014-fellows-talks-session-1/" data-slug="from-3d-animated-molecules-to-tethered-kite-copters-a-recap-of-the-ted2014-fellows-talks-session-1">
			From 3D animated molecules to tethered kite-copters: A recap of the TED2014 Fellows Talks, Session&nbsp;1		</a>
	</h2>

	<div class="meta">
		<div class="meta__author">
			<span>By</span>
			<a href="http://blog.ted.com/author/mmechinita/">
				Karen Eng			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="meta__date">
			<span>on</span>
			<time datetime="2014-03-17" pubdate >
				Mar 17, 2014			</time>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="excerpt">
		<p>With the TED Fellows, expect the unexpected: 3D animated molecules, tethered quadcopter cameras, death row inmates turned lawyers, quantum chaos. It&#8217;s the fifth-anniversary edition of TED Fellows talks, live from Vancouver, and here&#8217;s what happened in Session 1. Usman Riaz, musician + artist The Fellows stage comes to life quietly with the melodic strains of <a class="read-more" title="Read more" href="http://blog.ted.com/2014/03/17/from-3d-animated-molecules-to-tethered-kite-copters-a-recap-of-the-ted2014-fellows-talks-session-1/">[<span>&hellip;</span>]</a></p>
	</div>

</article>
